description:

That's what Trevor had to say about Keith when they first met.

"Nah," Trevor said (he's kind of shy). "I don't have to. He's hot."
I knew they were hitting it off. Keith was sneaking glances at Trevor's muscles.
What wasn't surprising was that Trevor came out of his shell when he got naked and got his dick hard.
He's quite the fuck machine!
title: Trevor & Keith
